    <item>
      <title>舒尔茨经济顾问库基斯将成为新任财政部长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/scholz-economic-adviser-kukies-to-become-new-finance-minister</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据一位不愿透露姓名的政府官员透露，德国总理奥拉夫·朔尔茨的经济顾问约尔格·库基斯将接替克里斯蒂安·林德纳担任财政部长。由于讨论机密计划，该官员不愿透露姓名。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/scholz-economic-adviser-kukies-to-become-new-finance-minister</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Nov 2024 07:58:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>6500 亿欧元外流是德国政治动荡的核心</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/germany-s-capital-exodus-is-at-the-heart-of-coalition-collapse</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国总理奥拉夫·舒尔茨领导的分裂联盟难以阻止大规模的资本流失，而唐纳德·特朗普连任后，资本流失可能会加速。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/germany-s-capital-exodus-is-at-the-heart-of-coalition-collapse</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Nov 2024 06:51:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国社交媒体对特朗普复出表示钦佩</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/chinese-social-media-buzzes-with-admiration-for-trump-s-comeback</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国社交媒体用户对唐纳德·特朗普的惊人总统复出表示欢迎，但同时也承认共和党的政治复兴可能意味着世界第二大经济体将面临更多动荡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/chinese-social-media-buzzes-with-admiration-for-trump-s-comeback</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Nov 2024 05:39:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>莫桑比克反对派领导人放弃重返抗议的计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/mozambican-opposition-head-scraps-plan-to-return-before-protest</link>
      <description><![CDATA[莫桑比克反对党领导人放弃了周四返回进行最后游行的计划。反对党领导人的支持者因上个月有争议的选举而举行抗议活动，震惊了这个东南部非洲国家。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/mozambican-opposition-head-scraps-plan-to-return-before-protest</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Nov 2024 05:20:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
