      <title>韩国外长尹永康与特朗普讨论平壤军队问题</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/south-korea-s-yoon-discusses-pyongyang-s-troop-moves-with-trump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在人们对平壤与莫斯科不断深化的军事合作日益担忧的背景下，韩国总统尹锡烈与美国当选总统唐纳德·特朗普在电话交谈中讨论了朝鲜军队在俄罗斯的存在问题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/south-korea-s-yoon-discusses-pyongyang-s-troop-moves-with-trump</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Nov 2024 02:00:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>舒尔茨呼吁提前举行德国大选，因执政联盟已破裂</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/scholz-fires-finance-minister-raising-prospect-of-new-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于在如何重振低迷的经济问题上产生分歧，德国总理奥拉夫·朔尔茨 (Olaf Scholz) 领导的三党执政联盟解体，呼吁提前举行选举。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/scholz-fires-finance-minister-raising-prospect-of-new-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 19:54:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普复出让英国明星陷入尴尬关系</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/trump-comeback-traps-uk-s-starmer-in-uncomfortable-relationship</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普曾多次告诉英国的同事，他认为英国新任首相基尔·斯塔默“非常左翼”，强调美国和英国传统上密切的关系可能因共和党当选总统周二的胜利而变得紧张。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/trump-comeback-traps-uk-s-starmer-in-uncomfortable-relationship</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 16:31:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尽管 60% 的关税可能带来混乱，但习近平已为应对特朗普做好了更充分的准备</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/xi-is-better-prepared-for-trump-even-as-60-tariffs-risk-chaos</link>
      <description><![CDATA[2018 年，当唐纳德·特朗普首次与中国发起贸易战时，北京发现自己处于劣势，不知道该如何应对。这一次，习近平主席做好了更充分的准备，尽管他可能会失去更多。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/xi-is-better-prepared-for-trump-even-as-60-tariffs-risk-chaos</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 11:45:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
